In old time data can be store using File Based System 
       For Ex- Excel , Word Docx etc 
       Problems 
       1. Data Redundancy
       2. Data Inconsistency
       3. Difficult Data Access
       4. Security
       

Database introduced so it can solves all the problems that can comes in File Based System 

Database - It is a collection of related data.
           It helps to solve the problem of Data Redundancy and Data Inconsistency.
           (Store the data once and we can use it anywhere that we want)

           It also helps to easy Apps Integration
           Easy data Access
           Provides Security